headline: Skyworks Solutions Stockholders Approve Share Issuance Proposal at Virtual Special Meeting
summary: Skyworks Solutions (NASDAQ:SWKS) held a virtual special meeting of stockholders chaired by President and CEO Phil Brace, with Senior Vice President, General Counsel, and Secretary Robert Terry and Vice President, Associate General Counsel, and Assistant Secretary David Chase also participating.
